    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that won't drain your wallet? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives well, making it a solid choice for everyday commuting and errands. You'll notice some cosmetic wear consistent with normal use, but mechanically it's up to the task. If you're after reliable transportation at an honest price, this one's worth a serious look!",
